Package: resources
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Monitor for system resources and processes
 Resources is a simple yet powerful monitor for system resources and processes,
 written in Rust and using GTK 4 and Libadwaita.
 .
 It provides a modern user interface to view CPU, memory, and network usage,
 as well as managing running processes.